rComments: Dr. Wyatt is very knowledgeable about the field of journalism and has a lot of insight into the field! However, the ways in which Dr. Wyatt goes about sharing this insight and knowledge can make him come off as harsh and unapproachable. He's a tough grader and can be very critical of students' work.
Make sure you do your readings, and you'll be fine! Prof Wyatt's love of the material is obvious. Very approachable. Take his class!

Great Professor. He is very passionate about what he teaches and wants to share that passion with his class, but only if they read!!! He knows how to keep the class engaged and interested. If you keep up with the readings and put your best effort forward, you're golden.
